Author: superymir
Text: thank you so much, i didn't even know EDNOS was a thing until now.

Author: 3-months-to-45
Text: Remember, just because you don't cleanly fit into a certain definition does not invalidate your ED. Even if it's no longer exactly bulimia, EDNOS can be equally, if not even more serious. I struggled with feeling like an imposter for a really long time too, even to this day, so you definitely aren't alone in that.
